Matlab - unit properties analysis notes

-first run:
concatDataIncludeSpeed.m
-save fig if you want (e.g., 000_concat.fig)

-next run:
analyzeUnitMaxMin.m (script analyzes unit properties like peak-trough width, amplitude and amplitude ratio)
-save fig if you want (e.g., 000_unit_pt.fig)

analyzeUnitISIetc.m (scrpt analyzes further properties like ISI, colors unit width points depending on ISI and generates ISI histograms)
-save fig if you want (e.g., 000_unit_pt_2colors.fig, 000_unit_width_ISI.fig, 000_unit_ISI_10ms.fig)
